# Vim configuration

My personal Vim configuration

### Installation guide

* Backup your current directory

`mv ~/.vim ~/.vim_bak`

* Clone this repository to your .vim directory

`git clone git://github.com/DoesntMatter/vimrc.git ~/.vim`

* Link your .vimrc

`ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc`

* Update this repository

`cd ~/.vim && git pull`

